Package rekit.logic.gameelements.inanimate

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BoostBox
    This Box realizes an Inanimate which boosts the Player from time to time.
    ClimbUpBox
    This Box realizes an Inanimate which the Player can climb up.
    EndTrigger
    This class represents an EndPortal.
    Inanimate
    This is the default implementation of an inanimate in the game.
    InanimateBox
    This is the default implementation of an inanimate in the game (no ground).
    InanimateDoor
    This is the default implementation of an inanimate door in the game.
    InanimateFloor
    The standard Inanimate that will be used for the lowest height in the level.
    InanimateTrigger
    This is the default implementation of an inanimate trigger in the game.
    MovingBox
    As the class name already said; this Class realizes a moving box.
    The Player can jump on it to solve a level
    ReflectionBox
    This class realizes a Box which will "reflect" your Player.
    ToggleBox
    This class realizes a box which toggles between solid an not-solid state from time to time.
